{
  "chapter": 86,
  "chapter_summary": "第八十六回“错的是谁呢”主要描写了李寻欢与上官金虹在金钱帮总部的一场对峙。上官金虹的居所极其简陋，仿佛坟墓，他以此彰显自己的冷酷与警觉。两人展开了一场关于生死、清醒与痛苦的哲学辩论。李寻欢在死亡面前表现出豁达与洒脱，反而让上官金虹感到不安。随后，场景转到林诗音与龙小云母子。龙小云得知母亲要拿怜花宝典去救李寻欢，内心充满痛苦与嫉妒，甚至坦言恨李寻欢。最后，龙啸云出现，他抢走怜花宝典，试图用自己的命换取妻儿的幸福，展现了悲剧性的父爱。整章通过复杂的人物关系，探讨了愧疚、牺牲与命运的无解之谜。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这地方你满意了么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这地方至少很干燥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "的确很干燥，我可以保证连一滴水都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这地方一向没有茶，没有水，没有酒，也从来没有人在这里流过一滴眼泪。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "血呢？有没有人在这里流过血？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "也没有——就算有人想死在这里，还没有走到这里之前，血就已流干了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我若不想要他进来，无论他是死是活，都休想走进这屋子。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "老实说，活着住在这里虽然不舒服，但死在这里倒不错。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "因为这地方本来就像是坟墓。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "既然你喜欢，我不妨就将你埋在这里。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "清醒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为我若不能保持清醒，也一样会被人踩在脚下的，一想到你的榜样，我当然就能警惕自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "但一个人清醒的时候若是太多了，岂非也痛苦得很？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我不会痛苦，从来没有过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "那只因你也从来没有快乐过……有时我很想问问你，你究竟是为了什么而活着的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "有些人也许真不知道自己是为了什么而活着的，但还有些却更可怜，他们甚至不知道自己是为了什么而死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "也许你就不知道自己是为了什么而死的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "也许我根本不想知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你不想？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "因为我已知道死也并不是什么大不了的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "在你眼中，看来我现在已经是个死人了，是不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你倒很有自知之明。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "既然我已死定了，就不必再为任何事操心，也不再烦恼，你呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "现在我想坐，就坐下来，想闭起眼睛，你能不能？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你当然不能，因为你还要担心很多事，还要提防我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "所以，至少现在我总比你舒服多了。",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我既然已答应过不让你湿淋淋地死，本想等你衣服一干透就出手的，可是现在我主意又变了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "现在我不但要给你套干净的衣服，还要给你一壶酒，因为你说的话实在很有趣，能听到死人说如此有趣的话，实在不容易。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "text": "你是不是一直都在后面跟着我？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "拿去。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "text": "这是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "你不知道这是什么？你岂非正是为了要拿这东西才回来的么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "text": "我……我是回来看你的。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "若不是为了这东西，你还会回来看我？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "你本就打算离开我，若不是为了这样东西，你只怕早就走了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "text": "我的确准备到一个很远很远的地方去，可是我……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "用不着你说，我也知道你要到哪里去。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "text": "你知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "你要去救李寻欢，是不是？",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "你准备用这本怜花宝典去救李寻欢，是不是？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "那么你为什么还不拿去？为什么还不去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "有了这本怜花宝典，上官金虹一定会见你的，因为他也是练武的，见了这种东西也会心动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "你想利用这机会跟他拼命，但你当然也知道要他死并不容易，所以你这么做，只不过是想将他先抱住，能将他多抱住一刻，李寻欢就能多活一刻，阿飞也许就能及时赶去救他！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "李寻欢的确对你很好，你为了他就算连自己的儿子、自己的性命都不要了，也没有人能说你不对。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "可是你有没有替别人想过，有没有替我想过，我毕竟是你的儿子……我……我……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "text": "我当然也替你想过，我……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "你替我想过，我知道，你要我明天早上到那里去等他们，你既已为他死了，他们见到我，自然一定会好好地照顾我。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "可是你又怎知一定能救得了他呢？他若看到你死了，心里岂非更乱，更难受？就算阿飞能赶去，他也未必能活得了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "何况，就算他能活下去，就算他肯照顾我，我也不会跟着他的，我根本连看都不愿看他一眼。",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "因为我恨他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "我恨他并不是因为他废了我的武功。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "text": "那么你是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "我恨他为什么不是我的父亲，我也恨我自己为什么不是他的儿子。我若是他的儿子，你岂非就不会离开我了，一切事岂非全都会好得多？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "text": "孩子，我对不起你，对不起你……像我们这样的父母，做我们的孩子实在不容易……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "你并没有对不起他，是我对不起你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "text": "我知道，你不愿做我的儿子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "我也知道你不愿做我的妻子，我这人活着本就是多余的。",
      "tone": "绝望",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "可是我却一心要做你们的好父亲、好丈夫，只不过……看来我并没有做好，我什么事全都做错了。",
      "tone": "自责",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "text": "我也对不起你，我也没有做你的好妻子。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "这不能怪你，只怪我，我若没有遇见你，没有遇见李寻欢，你们全都不会变成这样子，全都会很幸福。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "text": "无论你做过什么事，你至少也是为了要保护你的家，保护你的妻子，所以……你也没有错，我绝不能怪你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "也许我们都没有错，那么错的是谁呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "我本不想再来见你们的，这次你出来，我就知道你已下了决心要离开我，所以我既没有劝你留下，也不想求你回去，因为……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "我自己也知道我所做的那些事，不但令你伤心，也令你失望，但我还是忍不住要偷偷地跟你们出来，只要能远远地看你们一眼，我就满足。",
      "tone": "深情",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "text": "求求你不要再说了，求求你……",
      "tone": "哀求",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "我的确不该再说了，因为现在无论说什么都已太迟。",
      "tone": "绝望",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "text": "你知道，我欠他的太多，我不能眼看着他死。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "我也欠他的，欠得更多，所以，有些事你应该让我去做。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "text": "你想做什么？你难道……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "你不能死，也不应该死，该死的是我，我活着，大家都痛苦，我死了，你们反而能好好地活下去。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "text": "孩子，好好照顾你的母亲，至于我这父亲……你承不承认都没关系。",
      "tone": "慈爱",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun_son",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun_father",
      "text": "我承认，只有你才是我的父亲，我也只愿意做你的儿子，除了你，什么人我都不要，无论什么人……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 86,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    }
